<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{ event_name }}</title>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            background: #f5f5f5;
            color: #333;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .container {
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 600px;
            padding: 2rem;
        }
        .logo {
            max-width: 320px;
            width: 100%;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        .tagline {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #fff;
            background: {{ primary_color }};
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-decoration: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: opacity 0.2s;
        }
        .btn:hover { opacity: 0.9; }
        .info {
            margin-top: 3rem;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-align: left;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .info h2 {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
            color: {{ primary_color }};
        }
        .info p { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: #555; }
        .cert-note {
            margin-top: 2rem;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: #999;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <img src="/static/logo-text.svg" alt="{{ event_name }}" class="logo">
        <p class="tagline">{{ event_tagline }}</p>
        <a href="https://{{ domain }}/_matrix/client/v3/login/sso/redirect?redirectUrl=https%3A%2F%2F{{ domain }}%2Felement%2F" class="btn">
            Start Chatting
        </a>
        <div class="info">
            <h2>How it works</h2>
            <p><strong>No passwords needed.</strong> This chat uses passkeys &mdash; your device&rsquo;s biometric or PIN &mdash; to sign you in.</p>
            <p><strong>New here?</strong> Click &ldquo;Start Chatting&rdquo; and then &ldquo;Register&rdquo; to create your account with a passkey.</p>
            <p><strong>Returning?</strong> Click &ldquo;Start Chatting&rdquo; and your browser will prompt for your passkey.</p>
        </div>
        <p class="cert-note">
            This service uses a self-signed certificate. Your browser may show a security warning &mdash; this is expected for local deployments.
        </p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
